index_struct.text: The summaries of these documents are that they provide an overview of the purpose of the experimental folder, which is to provide a space for experiments, cool ideas, and other projects that are not yet ready to be included in the core abstractions. If the project is found to be interesting and validated, then it can be moved into the core abstractions.

🧪  Experimental

This section is for experiments, cool ideas, and more! 

Code here lives outside the base package. If a project is sufficiently interesting and validated, then we will move it into the core abstractions.
